body_html: The tensorflow graph being supplied as an input is custom code. We need much information in cases like these to determine if it's a bug. Sometimes issues like these happen when migrating pbtxt files between TF versions. I can reopen if you can help us understand the bug. Otherwise please try StackOverflow.
